{"typeId":"superai","title":"SuperAI","subtitle":"composite","icon":"\uD83E\uDDBE","category":"Ai","description":"An AI that reads the chat it has seen, can fetch older history (even from before it joined), and reacts to a specific message by id - assembled from nodes you can edit. Right-click -\u003E Edit to rewire it. Add an OpenAI key as a secret named \u0027openai\u0027, set a goal, and wire \u0027reply\u0027 into Send Reply.","inputs":[{"name":"","kind":"Exec"}],"outputs":[{"name":"then","kind":"Exec"},{"name":"reply","kind":"Text"}],"params":[{"key":"model","label":"Model","type":"Text","default":"gpt-4o-mini"},{"key":"system","label":"System","type":"Text","default":"You are ircuitry, a friendly IRC bot. Use your tools to inspect recent messages or fetch older history, then react to the right message by its id. Keep any text short."},{"key":"goal","label":"Goal","type":"Text","default":"{nick} said: {message}\nDecide what to do."}],"subgraph":{
